      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you decide to purchase. The exterior shows its age \u2014 you'll notice several scratches and minor dents consistent with years of regular use, though no major structural damage. The interior has visible wear on the seats and trim, and some surfaces show fading or scuffing, but everything remains functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some routine maintenance or minor repairs in the near future. This is a solid option for a buyer who wants a dependable daily driver without paying a premium price, and who doesn't mind cosmetic imperfections. What you see is what you get \u2014 no hidden surprises.",
