    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This is a truly exceptional vehicle being offered in mint condition \u2014 one of the finest examples you'll find on the market today. The car presents beautifully inside and out, with paintwork that retains a deep, lustrous finish free of scratches, chips, or blemishes. The interior is immaculate: all surfaces, upholstery, and trim are in like-new condition with no wear, staining, or damage to speak of. Mechanically, the car is in outstanding shape \u2014 the engine runs smoothly and powerfully, all systems function exactly as intended, and there are no warning lights, leaks, or unusual noises. Service history is well-maintained, and the vehicle has been carefully looked after throughout its life. Tires have strong tread remaining, brakes are in excellent condition, and all electronics and features operate flawlessly. This is the kind of car you can drive home with complete confidence and zero immediate expenses. Serious buyers who appreciate a truly turn-key, top-condition vehicle will not be disappointed \u2014 this one is the real deal.",
      "price": 47500.0,
